Vernacular names and uses.
– “Hazoala” (
Randrianaivo et al. 2364
); “Lalampito” (
Service Forestier 7775
); “Lampivahatry” (
Randrianaivo et al. 2364
); “Lapivahatra” (
Ramison & Armand 313
); “Lohariana” (
Réserves Naturelles 3813
); “Menaky” (
